summary: This is simply a Zelda preset i made as requested by lefttounge
descriptionHtml:
I originally wasn't going to create a Zelda Preset but i decided to fulfill a request from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/14336449]lefttounge[/url] as i said i would.this took roughly an hour and a half. as usual you are welcome to modify and upload to NEXUS as long as you give me credit. you are welcome to create a follower from this as long as you give me credit. and Din forbid don't upload this anywhere else! she is a[b][i][u] B[/u][/i][/b][i][b][u]reton[/u][/b][/i].
